data.description: Urban Living in Walkable Downtown Fort Worth! Freshly polished concrete floors. Granite countertops in kitchen and bathroom. Spacious bedroom with walk in closet! All new items include appliances, HVAC, water heater and even the furniture with warranty on all! Large beautiful windows with plenty of natural light. Onsite amenities galore, including 24 hour professional concierge, indoor pool, gym, restaurant and bar. No need to drive when you can hop on the train located downstairs at the train station. Relax in the park located adjacent to the parking lot. Plenty of nearby restaurants, shops and entertainment are all within walking distance! Two unassigned parking spots issued by HOA with permit. All furnishings except the bed are available for a fee.
